articles.author: Irene Loewenson
articles.title: At least 3 Marines killed, more injured in Osprey crash in Australia - Marine Corps Times
articles.description: Five others were in serious condition, and others unaccounted for, after an MV-22 Osprey crashed with 23 service members aboard.
articles.content:
Three Marines have been confirmed dead after a Marine Corps MV-22 Osprey carrying 23 service members crashed in Australia on Sunday.
Five others in serious condition were transported to Royal Darwin… [+2816 chars]
